00:01:27,164 --> 00:01:30,084
EPISODE 10

4
00:01:50,244 --> 00:01:52,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Among these cards,
which has the highest value?</b></font>

5
00:01:56,684 --> 00:01:58,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ace of Diamonds.</b></font>

6
00:01:58,764 --> 00:01:59,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you sure?</b></font>

7
00:02:00,244 --> 00:02:01,164
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm sure.</b></font>

8
00:02:03,084 --> 00:02:04,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hearts...</b></font>

9
00:02:05,364 --> 00:02:06,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Jack of Hearts.</b></font>

10
00:02:10,044 --> 00:02:11,404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Clubs...</b></font>

11
00:02:13,484 --> 00:02:15,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>King of Clubs.</b></font>

12
00:02:21,444 --> 00:02:22,564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Diamonds.</b></font>

13
00:02:24,524 --> 00:02:25,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Spades...</b></font>

14
00:02:26,724 --> 00:02:27,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Queen of Spades.</b></font>

15
00:02:47,004 --> 00:02:47,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Am I wrong again?</b></font>

16
00:02:48,604 --> 00:02:50,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No, but you're too slow.</b></font>

17
00:02:51,084 --> 00:02:53,564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey, it's quite amazing
that I didn't make a mistake, okay?</b></font>

18
00:03:00,004 --> 00:03:01,284
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll do better.</b></font>

19
00:03:01,924 --> 00:03:03,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Since you already know the basics,</b></font>

20
00:03:03,804 --> 00:03:05,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>the biggest problem now</b></font>

21
00:03:05,444 --> 00:03:07,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>is that you always expose
the cards you have.</b></font>

22
00:03:08,844 --> 00:03:09,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No way.</b></font>

23
00:03:10,404 --> 00:03:11,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You have a lot of spades.</b></font>

24
00:03:13,364 --> 00:03:14,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Am I right?</b></font>

25
00:03:15,924 --> 00:03:17,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're insanely good at this.</b></font>

26
00:03:17,924 --> 00:03:19,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Try to bluff and see if you can fool me.</b></font>

27
00:03:19,804 --> 00:03:21,444
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you can do that,
then we stand a chance.</b></font>

28
00:03:23,924 --> 00:03:24,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right.</b></font>

29
00:03:26,684 --> 00:03:28,564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you like studying at Mingde University?</b></font>

30
00:03:28,964 --> 00:03:30,044
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes.</b></font>

31
00:03:30,484 --> 00:03:32,284
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The people here are really amazing.</b></font>

32
00:03:32,844 --> 00:03:33,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You don't like it here.</b></font>

33
00:03:34,604 --> 00:03:36,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That doesn't count. You already know that.</b></font>

34
00:03:37,164 --> 00:03:38,404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you like Si?</b></font>

35
00:03:39,324 --> 00:03:40,444
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Of course not.</b></font>

36
00:03:41,044 --> 00:03:42,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I asked you to fool me.</b></font>

37
00:03:42,364 --> 00:03:44,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you don't like him,
you should have said that you do.</b></font>

38
00:03:45,284 --> 00:03:46,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I couldn't make myself say that.</b></font>

39
00:03:46,724 --> 00:03:48,044
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then do you like me?</b></font>

40
00:03:53,484 --> 00:03:54,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No.</b></font>

41
00:03:55,964 --> 00:03:57,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That seems like the truth.</b></font>

42
00:03:57,764 --> 00:03:59,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's not true.</b></font>

43
00:03:59,164 --> 00:04:00,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I was just kidding.</b></font>

44
00:04:08,284 --> 00:04:10,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Who asks questions like that?</b></font>

45
00:04:10,324 --> 00:04:11,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How can I answer that?</b></font>

46
00:04:12,684 --> 00:04:13,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Only you can't.</b></font>

47
00:04:15,524 --> 00:04:16,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then do you like Jing?</b></font>

48
00:04:22,404 --> 00:04:23,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sorry.</b></font>

49
00:04:23,884 --> 00:04:25,564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I shouldn't have asked that question.</b></font>

50
00:04:27,524 --> 00:04:29,564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If I say I'm already over her,
would you believe me?</b></font>

51
00:04:34,924 --> 00:04:36,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you want me to stay here?</b></font>

52
00:04:37,684 --> 00:04:38,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes.</b></font>

53
00:04:39,684 --> 00:04:41,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then I'll do my best to stay,</b></font>

54
00:04:41,844 --> 00:04:43,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>so that I can do everything
to protect you.</b></font>

55
00:05:20,484 --> 00:05:21,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If Shancai leaves Mingde,</b></font>

56
00:05:22,484 --> 00:05:23,444
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll leave F4.</b></font>

57
00:05:26,404 --> 00:05:27,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you know what you're saying?</b></font>

58
00:05:31,684 --> 00:05:34,564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Although it's cool to be a part of F4,</b></font>

59
00:05:35,244 --> 00:05:38,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>if you bully Shancai, you're my enemy.</b></font>

60
00:05:39,524 --> 00:05:42,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Qinghe, you're not that important.</b></font>

61
00:05:43,484 --> 00:05:45,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And Shancai doesn't even like you.</b></font>

62
00:05:46,644 --> 00:05:48,404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That doesn't matter.</b></font>

63
00:05:48,564 --> 00:05:49,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I like Shancai.</b></font>

64
00:05:50,964 --> 00:05:53,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If I expect the person I like
to like me as well,</b></font>

65
00:05:53,764 --> 00:05:54,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>that's not manly at all.</b></font>

66
00:05:58,204 --> 00:05:59,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Daoming Si.</b></font>

67
00:05:59,604 --> 00:06:02,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you like Shancai,
you have to treat her nicely.</b></font>

68
00:06:03,444 --> 00:06:04,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Even if Shancai doesn't like you,</b></font>

69
00:06:05,684 --> 00:06:07,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>it should be enough for you
to see her happy,</b></font>

70
00:06:08,364 --> 00:06:09,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>isn't it?</b></font>

71
00:06:10,484 --> 00:06:14,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Qinghe, I suddenly realized
that you have the potential to join F4.</b></font>

72
00:06:15,364 --> 00:06:17,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What you just said is very manly.</b></font>

73
00:06:18,404 --> 00:06:19,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Start practicing how to play Bridge.</b></font>

74
00:06:20,444 --> 00:06:22,404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This way, if F4 really loses a member,</b></font>

75
00:06:23,124 --> 00:06:26,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>at least we can have a full team
in competitions.</b></font>

76
00:06:36,724 --> 00:06:38,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>From the very first day
I entered Mingde University,</i></b></font>

77
00:06:39,084 --> 00:06:42,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I heard about all sorts of bets made
when playing against F4.</i></b></font>

78
00:06:42,684 --> 00:06:44,284
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I never imagined</i></b></font>

79
00:06:44,604 --> 00:06:47,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I'd receive a joker card
to fight Daoming Si</i></b></font>

80
00:06:48,004 --> 00:06:50,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>with Huaze Lei on my side
during my freshman year.</i></b></font>

81
00:06:54,724 --> 00:06:56,164
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Who do you think will win?</b></font>

82
00:06:57,284 --> 00:06:59,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Daoming Si, of course.</b></font>

83
00:06:59,204 --> 00:07:00,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai doesn't know how to play Bridge.</b></font>

84
00:07:00,964 --> 00:07:04,404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Even if Huaze Lei is amazing at it,
she'll be useless.</b></font>

85
00:07:05,484 --> 00:07:06,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai.</b></font>

86
00:07:08,164 --> 00:07:09,564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do your best. I hope you'll win.</b></font>

87
00:07:10,764 --> 00:07:11,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Look.</b></font>

88
00:07:11,684 --> 00:07:12,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b>SHANCAI, YOU CAN DO IT</b></font>

89
00:07:24,844 --> 00:07:26,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Did you sleep well last night?</b></font>

90
00:07:26,204 --> 00:07:28,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm so nervous.
I didn't sleep well at all.</b></font>

91
00:07:29,844 --> 00:07:30,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't be scared.</b></font>

92
00:07:34,884 --> 00:07:37,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Actually, I slept really well.
I fooled you, right?</b></font>

93
00:07:38,164 --> 00:07:40,284
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes, you did.
You can make it on your own now.</b></font>

94
00:07:43,924 --> 00:07:45,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then do we stand a chance now?</b></font>

95
00:07:45,964 --> 00:07:46,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>My gosh!</b></font>

96
00:07:47,204 --> 00:07:50,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Why are they holding hands?
-Right?</b></font>

97
00:08:05,164 --> 00:08:06,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai.</b></font>

98
00:08:06,244 --> 00:08:09,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Welcome to the Bridge Room and to
the two-on-two competition against the F4.</b></font>

99
00:08:10,244 --> 00:08:11,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Did Huaze Lei explain the rules to you?</b></font>

100
00:08:13,084 --> 00:08:13,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes.</b></font>

101
00:08:14,004 --> 00:08:16,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you plan to hold hands
while playing Bridge?</b></font>

102
00:08:19,364 --> 00:08:21,404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si will play with Meizuo,
and Shancai with Lei.</b></font>

103
00:08:21,484 --> 00:08:23,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The two teams will take turns dealing.</b></font>

104
00:08:23,204 --> 00:08:24,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Six tricks will be added
to the card they have called.</b></font>

105
00:08:24,844 --> 00:08:28,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Win the number you bid or more,
and you win the game. Otherwise, you lose.</b></font>

106
00:08:28,924 --> 00:08:29,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are we clear?</b></font>

107
00:08:31,844 --> 00:08:32,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes.</b></font>

108
00:08:33,644 --> 00:08:34,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Please have a seat.</b></font>

109
00:08:44,124 --> 00:08:45,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You know what's at stake, right?</b></font>

110
00:08:48,684 --> 00:08:49,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't we all?</b></font>

111
00:08:51,724 --> 00:08:52,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What's at stake here?</b></font>

112
00:08:54,564 --> 00:08:56,164
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, tell them.</b></font>

113
00:09:02,684 --> 00:09:03,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What's at stake</b></font>

114
00:09:05,364 --> 00:09:06,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>is that if I win,</b></font>

115
00:09:07,524 --> 00:09:08,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you have to forgive me.</b></font>

116
00:09:14,564 --> 00:09:16,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Is it that important to you?</b></font>

117
00:09:18,764 --> 00:09:19,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes.</b></font>

118
00:09:20,124 --> 00:09:21,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>From what I can see,</b></font>

119
00:09:21,964 --> 00:09:25,044
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you just want to be free from guilt
when you're in a relationship with Lei.</b></font>

120
00:09:26,644 --> 00:09:27,564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Maybe.</b></font>

121
00:09:28,444 --> 00:09:29,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then I definitely refuse to lose.</b></font>

122
00:09:30,924 --> 00:09:32,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What if I win?</b></font>

123
00:09:34,524 --> 00:09:35,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then I won't see Shancai again.</b></font>

124
00:09:41,404 --> 00:09:42,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You said that on your own accord.</b></font>

125
00:09:43,524 --> 00:09:45,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes, I did.</b></font>

126
00:09:46,404 --> 00:09:47,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But I might not lose.</b></font>

127
00:09:48,324 --> 00:09:49,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Right?</b></font>

128
00:09:50,564 --> 00:09:51,404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes.</b></font>

129
00:09:53,964 --> 00:09:55,564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. Let the competition begin.</b></font>

130
00:10:02,084 --> 00:10:03,044
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Please check your cards.</b></font>

131
00:10:11,364 --> 00:10:13,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, you can call your card first.</b></font>

132
00:10:17,444 --> 00:10:18,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>One of Hearts.</b></font>

133
00:10:19,524 --> 00:10:20,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>One of Spades.</b></font>

134
00:10:21,844 --> 00:10:23,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Three of Hearts.</b></font>

135
00:10:23,164 --> 00:10:24,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>What?</i></b></font>

136
00:10:25,084 --> 00:10:27,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Huaze Lei is calling
the same Hearts suit as me?</i></b></font>

137
00:10:27,084 --> 00:10:29,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't have any Hearts cards.</b></font>

138
00:10:29,084 --> 00:10:31,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I just bluffed it initially.</b></font>

139
00:10:34,004 --> 00:10:34,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Four of Clubs.</b></font>

140
00:10:35,604 --> 00:10:37,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Daoming Si is calling four of Clubs now.</i></b></font>

141
00:10:38,724 --> 00:10:41,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>If I want to continue calling,
I have to go with four too.</i></b></font>

142
00:10:41,204 --> 00:10:44,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>That means I should at least
win ten tricks in order to win.</i></b></font>

143
00:10:45,204 --> 00:10:46,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I only have three Clubs cards.</i></b></font>

144
00:10:47,404 --> 00:10:50,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>If Huaze Lei also has them...</i></b></font>

145
00:11:01,324 --> 00:11:02,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The trump suit is Clubs.</b></font>

146
00:11:02,964 --> 00:11:04,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Huaze Lei, please proceed.</b></font>

147
00:11:10,604 --> 00:11:12,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, Lei made a mistake.</b></font>

148
00:11:13,524 --> 00:11:15,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He thinks that you have the ace of Hearts.</b></font>

149
00:11:15,764 --> 00:11:17,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's why he played the Hearts suit.</b></font>

150
00:11:17,524 --> 00:11:19,044
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He wants you to win the first trick.</b></font>

151
00:11:19,564 --> 00:11:21,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Actually, the ace of Hearts is with me.</b></font>

152
00:11:22,484 --> 00:11:24,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It looks like your plan
is not going to work.</b></font>

153
00:11:38,404 --> 00:11:41,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai has no Hearts. The trump suit,
two of Clubs, wins the first trick.</b></font>

154
00:11:44,364 --> 00:11:46,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, you did great.</b></font>

155
00:11:50,204 --> 00:11:53,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I never thought the innocent Shancai
would cheat.</b></font>

156
00:11:55,604 --> 00:11:57,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Even if Shancai cheats, she's still cute.</b></font>

157
00:11:58,364 --> 00:12:01,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Unlike others who tell the truth,
but always hurts people.</b></font>

158
00:12:06,324 --> 00:12:08,404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>A liar is more despicable, of course.</b></font>

159
00:12:09,684 --> 00:12:11,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Aren't you like that?</b></font>

160
00:12:12,724 --> 00:12:14,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Please note that this is a Bridge game.</b></font>

161
00:12:15,324 --> 00:12:16,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Refrain from verbal attacks.</b></font>

162
00:12:18,284 --> 00:12:20,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, the winner continues playing.</b></font>

163
00:12:36,604 --> 00:12:38,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai's ace of Diamonds beats you all.</b></font>

164
00:12:39,924 --> 00:12:42,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-She wins the second trick.
-Shancai, you're doing great.</b></font>

165
00:12:44,364 --> 00:12:45,444
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Huaze Lei taught me well.</b></font>

166
00:12:46,444 --> 00:12:47,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She's a quick study.</b></font>

167
00:12:50,164 --> 00:12:51,164
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Please continue.</b></font>

168
00:12:58,564 --> 00:13:00,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I won't let you two win again.</b></font>

169
00:13:01,204 --> 00:13:02,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Says who?</b></font>

170
00:13:02,684 --> 00:13:04,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We might not lose.</b></font>

171
00:13:05,764 --> 00:13:06,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>"We"?</b></font>

172
00:13:07,844 --> 00:13:08,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai.</b></font>

173
00:13:09,524 --> 00:13:11,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The "we" that you and Huaze Lei refer to</b></font>

174
00:13:11,404 --> 00:13:13,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>will soon disappear
from Mingde University.</b></font>

175
00:13:25,084 --> 00:13:26,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are they still not out?</b></font>

176
00:13:26,884 --> 00:13:29,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We finished the Big and Small game
in ten minutes.</b></font>

177
00:13:29,284 --> 00:13:33,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Qinghe, Shancai and Daoming Si
are playing an official game of Bridge.</b></font>

178
00:13:34,044 --> 00:13:35,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I know how to play that too.</b></font>

179
00:13:35,604 --> 00:13:38,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If I play them,
I'm sure F4 would surrender immediately.</b></font>

180
00:13:38,844 --> 00:13:40,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You silly boy.</b></font>

181
00:13:40,164 --> 00:13:43,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>F4 is the champion of countless
international Bridge competitions.</b></font>

182
00:13:44,004 --> 00:13:45,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Whom do you think you're fooling?</b></font>

183
00:13:46,004 --> 00:13:48,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Qinghe, I know that you
and Shancai are close.</b></font>

184
00:13:49,564 --> 00:13:51,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But even so, you have to face reality.</b></font>

185
