00:24:30,844 --> 00:24:33,564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I wanted to speak to Shancai alone anyway.</b></font>

371
00:24:45,164 --> 00:24:46,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What did you want to speak to me about?</b></font>

372
00:24:47,284 --> 00:24:48,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not too sure either.</b></font>

373
00:24:48,924 --> 00:24:50,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I just want to talk to you alone.</b></font>

374
00:24:52,244 --> 00:24:54,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you want to suggest a topic
we can talk about?</b></font>

375
00:24:59,524 --> 00:25:00,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How about</b></font>

376
00:25:00,884 --> 00:25:02,284
<font color="#ffff00"><b>we talk about</b></font>

377
00:25:03,124 --> 00:25:04,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>our graduation trip?</b></font>

378
00:25:06,164 --> 00:25:08,164
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We went to Chongming Island</b></font>

379
00:25:08,764 --> 00:25:10,164
<font color="#ffff00"><b>for our graduation trip.</b></font>

380
00:25:11,364 --> 00:25:14,404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>At night, we had pillow fights.</b></font>

381
00:25:15,084 --> 00:25:16,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We also had a bonfire.</b></font>

382
00:25:17,684 --> 00:25:18,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When I think about it now,</b></font>

383
00:25:19,004 --> 00:25:20,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>it's still a very special memory.</b></font>

384
00:25:21,884 --> 00:25:23,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How about you? Where did you go?</b></font>

385
00:25:28,604 --> 00:25:29,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Prague.</b></font>

386
00:25:30,364 --> 00:25:31,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I've never been--</b></font>

387
00:25:36,524 --> 00:25:39,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you staring at me?</b></font>

388
00:25:40,804 --> 00:25:41,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're so ugly.</b></font>

389
00:25:43,924 --> 00:25:44,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Just kidding.</b></font>

390
00:25:46,444 --> 00:25:49,404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But when I look at you this way,
you're really ordinary</b></font>

391
00:25:49,604 --> 00:25:50,444
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and plain.</b></font>

392
00:25:52,964 --> 00:25:54,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You don't need to remind me, okay?</b></font>

393
00:26:01,564 --> 00:26:03,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>However, the way you looked
so serious during our game today</b></font>

394
00:26:05,084 --> 00:26:06,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>was mesmerizing.</b></font>

395
00:26:08,124 --> 00:26:11,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I never understood
why Si likes you so much before,</b></font>

396
00:26:13,564 --> 00:26:15,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>but I finally understood today.</b></font>

397
00:26:15,724 --> 00:26:16,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Actually...</b></font>

398
00:26:20,044 --> 00:26:21,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Actually, what?</b></font>

399
00:26:25,924 --> 00:26:27,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not sure how I feel about you.</b></font>

400
00:26:29,164 --> 00:26:30,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ximen said</b></font>

401
00:26:30,764 --> 00:26:32,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>it may be because I'm still hurt
about Jing,</b></font>

402
00:26:33,884 --> 00:26:35,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and that I'm using you to forget her.</b></font>

403
00:26:37,244 --> 00:26:38,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Maybe.</b></font>

404
00:26:39,484 --> 00:26:40,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>However...</b></font>

405
00:26:42,124 --> 00:26:43,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's fine.</b></font>

406
00:26:43,564 --> 00:26:44,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I understand.</b></font>

407
00:26:45,884 --> 00:26:48,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I know how you feel about Jing.</b></font>

408
00:26:49,564 --> 00:26:53,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I also know how special she is to you.</b></font>

409
00:27:10,684 --> 00:27:12,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you alone again?</b></font>

410
00:27:14,684 --> 00:27:16,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I looked for you for so long,
my legs are tired.</b></font>

411
00:27:19,364 --> 00:27:21,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>From now on, don't hide
from us again, okay?</b></font>

412
00:27:24,284 --> 00:27:25,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you drawing?</b></font>

413
00:27:30,964 --> 00:27:32,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Is that me?</b></font>

414
00:27:34,364 --> 00:27:36,444
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It really looks like me.
I like it so much.</b></font>

415
00:27:39,644 --> 00:27:42,404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When I was little, everyone mocked me
and said my drawings were ugly.</b></font>

416
00:27:43,324 --> 00:27:44,284
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Except Jing.</b></font>

417
00:27:48,404 --> 00:27:51,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Jing is a really special person.</b></font>

418
00:27:53,604 --> 00:27:56,404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not sure if I can love
another person again.</b></font>

419
00:27:59,884 --> 00:28:01,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Although I really like you,</b></font>

420
00:28:02,324 --> 00:28:04,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I know it's not love.</b></font>

421
00:28:08,804 --> 00:28:10,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's fine.</b></font>

422
00:28:12,404 --> 00:28:13,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sorry.</b></font>

423
00:28:14,684 --> 00:28:16,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you apologizing to me?</b></font>

424
00:28:17,444 --> 00:28:20,404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If I didn't come back,
you could've been with Si.</b></font>

425
00:28:21,724 --> 00:28:23,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You don't have to apologize to me.</b></font>

426
00:28:24,004 --> 00:28:25,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Who would want to be with him?</b></font>

427
00:28:27,684 --> 00:28:28,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And...</b></font>

428
00:28:30,084 --> 00:28:31,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>if this hadn't happened,</b></font>

429
00:28:33,004 --> 00:28:36,044
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I wouldn't have witnessed
the new person you are now.</b></font>

430
00:28:38,324 --> 00:28:39,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The new person?</b></font>

431
00:28:39,564 --> 00:28:40,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How am I different?</b></font>

432
00:28:45,044 --> 00:28:46,564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The old you</b></font>

433
00:28:47,324 --> 00:28:49,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>was very lazy.</b></font>

434
00:28:50,204 --> 00:28:51,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And the way you spoke was so cold.</b></font>

435
00:28:53,084 --> 00:28:54,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You seemed</b></font>

436
00:28:55,604 --> 00:28:56,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>very distant.</b></font>

437
00:28:57,844 --> 00:28:58,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Like this.</b></font>

438
00:29:01,204 --> 00:29:04,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>"I'm not interested
in other people's problems."</b></font>

439
00:29:09,644 --> 00:29:10,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You know,</b></font>

440
00:29:11,604 --> 00:29:13,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>every time you said</b></font>

441
00:29:13,164 --> 00:29:15,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>that other people's problems
were not your concern,</b></font>

442
00:29:16,524 --> 00:29:18,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I felt really sad.</b></font>

443
00:29:21,284 --> 00:29:23,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But you're completely different now.</b></font>

444
00:29:25,324 --> 00:29:27,284
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I like the new person you are now.</b></font>

445
00:29:30,724 --> 00:29:31,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm willing</b></font>

446
00:29:33,044 --> 00:29:34,564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>to be your good friend forever.</b></font>

447
00:29:55,244 --> 00:29:56,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thank you for being so understanding.</b></font>

448
00:30:11,244 --> 00:30:12,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm home.</b></font>

449
00:30:13,564 --> 00:30:15,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si, your sister, Shancai</b></font>

450
00:30:16,004 --> 00:30:18,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and your best friends are having
a gathering in the dining room.</b></font>

451
00:30:18,804 --> 00:30:20,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How dare they have a gathering here?</b></font>

452
00:30:26,764 --> 00:30:28,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're so close with my brother.</b></font>

453
00:30:28,084 --> 00:30:30,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why won't you teach him
how to get along with girls?</b></font>

454
00:30:31,204 --> 00:30:34,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ms. Zhuang, aside from you,</b></font>

455
00:30:34,284 --> 00:30:36,564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>what other girls can get along with Si?</b></font>

456
00:30:37,724 --> 00:30:39,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ms. Zhuang, it isn't just the girls.</b></font>

457
00:30:40,044 --> 00:30:40,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Even the guys.</b></font>

458
00:30:41,524 --> 00:30:44,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Aside from us,
no one wants to play with him.</b></font>

459
00:30:44,844 --> 00:30:45,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're right.</b></font>

460
00:30:46,284 --> 00:30:47,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We all inherited our mom's</b></font>

461
00:30:48,404 --> 00:30:51,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>bratty, difficult and
hard-to-get-along-with attitude.</b></font>

462
00:30:54,444 --> 00:30:56,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>As for Lei, even though
he's unpredictable,</b></font>

463
00:30:56,444 --> 00:30:58,284
<font color="#ffff00"><b>he has become very patient with her</b></font>

464
00:30:58,364 --> 00:30:59,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>once he liked her.</b></font>

465
00:31:00,164 --> 00:31:02,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No wonder we hear a "pow"</b></font>

466
00:31:02,124 --> 00:31:03,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>whenever Shancai sees Si.</b></font>

467
00:31:05,964 --> 00:31:08,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's like being in love with a time bomb.</b></font>

468
00:31:08,604 --> 00:31:10,164
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let my brother suffer a little.</b></font>

469
00:31:10,684 --> 00:31:12,564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sometimes, being heartbroken
is not a bad thing.</b></font>

470
00:31:14,844 --> 00:31:18,404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I wonder what Shancai and Lei</b></font>

471
00:31:18,804 --> 00:31:19,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>are doing right now.</b></font>

472
00:31:20,204 --> 00:31:21,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>They should be doing what they need to do.</b></font>

473
00:31:22,884 --> 00:31:23,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si.</b></font>

474
00:31:24,244 --> 00:31:26,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What does Si have to do
with what they're doing?</b></font>

475
00:31:26,764 --> 00:31:27,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What?</b></font>

476
00:31:46,964 --> 00:31:49,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si, why are you home so late?</b></font>

477
00:31:49,924 --> 00:31:51,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si, are you tired?</b></font>

478
00:31:51,364 --> 00:31:52,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you want to go get some rest?</b></font>

479
00:31:53,804 --> 00:31:55,044
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What were you talking about?</b></font>

480
00:31:56,844 --> 00:31:58,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We don't have to hide this from him.</b></font>

481
00:31:59,244 --> 00:32:00,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We have to tell him eventually.</b></font>

482
00:32:05,844 --> 00:32:06,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si.</b></font>

483
00:32:07,484 --> 00:32:09,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai and Lei
are in a bedroom right now.</b></font>

484
00:32:10,124 --> 00:32:13,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you're a real man,
you should be happy for them.</b></font>

485
00:32:17,924 --> 00:32:19,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why does it smell like gunpowder?</b></font>

486
00:32:20,404 --> 00:32:22,284
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I even hear the trigger for a bomb
being engaged.</b></font>

487
00:32:25,244 --> 00:32:27,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you think?
Is there anything you want to say?</b></font>

488
00:32:39,764 --> 00:32:42,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I never thought that Lei
had his ways with women.</b></font>

489
00:32:46,684 --> 00:32:48,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's a good thing, isn't it?</b></font>

490
00:32:51,204 --> 00:32:52,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's great, Si.</b></font>

491
00:32:53,124 --> 00:32:55,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-You're really over her.
-Si.</b></font>

492
00:32:55,844 --> 00:32:57,164
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're doing great.</b></font>

493
00:32:57,244 --> 00:32:59,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-You'll become a good man--
-Shut it!</b></font>

494
00:33:02,404 --> 00:33:03,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm starving.</b></font>

495
00:33:04,284 --> 00:33:05,284
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Get me something to eat.</b></font>

496
00:33:15,204 --> 00:33:16,284
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Lei.</i></b></font>

497
00:33:17,124 --> 00:33:19,044
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Thank you for telling me those things
last night.</i></b></font>

498
00:33:23,364 --> 00:33:24,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Jing.</i></b></font>

499
00:33:25,044 --> 00:33:27,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>It's true, I still can't compare to you.</i></b></font>

500
00:33:30,284 --> 00:33:31,444
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>But it doesn't matter.</i></b></font>

501
00:33:32,604 --> 00:33:33,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I'm Shancai, the weed.</i></b></font>

502
00:34:14,924 --> 00:34:17,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si, why are you up so early?</b></font>

503
00:34:20,324 --> 00:34:21,164
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ximen.</b></font>

504
00:34:22,844 --> 00:34:25,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you remember when I took
Lei's favorite toy?</b></font>

505
00:34:29,564 --> 00:34:30,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When was that?</b></font>

506
00:34:33,844 --> 00:34:35,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When we first entered grade school.</b></font>

507
00:34:36,044 --> 00:34:37,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I liked that autographed Spiderman</i></b></font>

508
00:34:38,164 --> 00:34:39,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>with the serial number.</i></b></font>

509
00:34:40,444 --> 00:34:41,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>If I had asked my dad,</i></b></font>

510
00:34:42,204 --> 00:34:44,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>he would've gotten it for me from the U.S.</i></b></font>

511
00:34:44,884 --> 00:34:46,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>As many as I wanted.</i></b></font>

512
00:34:48,564 --> 00:34:49,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you holding?</b></font>

513
00:34:50,244 --> 00:34:51,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let me see.</b></font>

514
00:34:51,844 --> 00:34:52,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Give it to me.</b></font>

515
00:34:52,924 --> 00:34:54,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>The more he treasured it,
the more I wanted it.</i></b></font>

516
00:34:55,844 --> 00:34:56,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I know</i></b></font>

517
00:34:57,324 --> 00:34:58,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>that I made an unforgivable mistake.</i></b></font>

518
00:35:02,764 --> 00:35:04,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You should've let go sooner!</b></font>

519
00:35:05,884 --> 00:35:07,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's all your fault.</b></font>

520
00:35:07,204 --> 00:35:08,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>But I just wouldn't admit it.</i></b></font>

521
00:35:11,084 --> 00:35:11,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>That night,</i></b></font>

522
00:35:13,444 --> 00:35:14,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I couldn't sleep.</i></b></font>

523
00:35:17,644 --> 00:35:20,044
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I thought that Lei would be mad
at me the next morning.</i></b></font>

524
00:35:22,004 --> 00:35:23,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So I planned to get you two</b></font>

525
00:35:24,964 --> 00:35:26,044
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and bully him the next day.</b></font>

526
00:35:28,884 --> 00:35:30,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's when I realized</b></font>

527
00:35:31,564 --> 00:35:33,444
<font color="#ffff00"><b>that I'd never be able to beat him.</b></font>

528
00:35:37,244 --> 00:35:38,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Nobody ever mentioned it again.</b></font>

529
00:35:40,244 --> 00:35:42,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Maybe Lei had also forgotten about it.</b></font>

530
00:35:46,124 --> 00:35:47,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But I still feel</b></font>

531
00:35:48,204 --> 00:35:49,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>that I owe him somehow.</b></font>

532
00:35:54,804 --> 00:35:55,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think...</b></font>

533
00:35:58,764 --> 00:36:00,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>it's time to make it up to him.</b></font>

534
00:36:03,804 --> 00:36:05,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you talking about Shancai?</b></font>

535
00:36:11,204 --> 00:36:12,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I shouldn't torment her anymore.</b></font>

536
00:36:52,124 --> 00:36:53,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, come here.</b></font>

537
00:36:53,484 --> 00:36:54,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We have something to tell you.</b></font>

538
00:37:01,484 --> 00:37:02,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Dad, Mom.</b></font>

539
00:37:02,644 --> 00:37:05,044
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sorry. I stayed over
at my friend's place last night.</b></font>

540
00:37:05,124 --> 00:37:06,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I wasn't able to tell you about it.</b></font>

541
00:37:08,084 --> 00:37:08,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai.</b></font>

542
00:37:09,204 --> 00:37:10,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You can't live here anymore.</b></font>

543
00:37:13,084 --> 00:37:13,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why?</b></font>

544
00:37:15,564 --> 00:37:17,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Your dad's moving into
a different company housing.</b></font>

545
00:37:19,044 --> 00:37:20,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where?</b></font>

546
00:37:26,444 --> 00:37:28,684
<font color="#ffff00"><b>"Great Earnings Investment
Consulting Corporation."</b></font>

547
00:37:29,564 --> 00:37:30,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Dad, really?</b></font>

548
00:37:31,404 --> 00:37:32,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's right.</b></font>

549
00:37:33,844 --> 00:37:35,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I had an interview a few days ago.</b></font>

550
00:37:36,844 --> 00:37:39,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The boss said that I have a lot
of potential in investment.</b></font>

551
00:37:40,764 --> 00:37:43,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Not only does this company
guarantee bonuses,</b></font>

552
00:37:43,804 --> 00:37:45,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b>the salaries are also guaranteed.</b></font>

553
00:37:45,884 --> 00:37:47,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm going to be rich.</b></font>

554
00:37:48,684 --> 00:37:50,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you know anything
about investment consulting?</b></font>

555
00:37:51,204 --> 00:37:53,044
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Right? I asked him the same thing.</b></font>

