578
00:38:57,164 --> 00:38:58,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Just throw them away.
-Throw them...</b></font>

579
00:38:59,404 --> 00:39:00,444
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Throw them away?</b></font>

580
00:39:01,244 --> 00:39:03,044
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Those are souvenirs of love.</b></font>

581
00:39:03,644 --> 00:39:04,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Throw them...</b></font>

582
00:39:05,204 --> 00:39:07,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, go and pack your things.</b></font>

583
00:39:07,284 --> 00:39:08,564
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We're moving tomorrow.</b></font>

584
00:39:09,164 --> 00:39:11,244
