595
00:39:47,684 --> 00:39:48,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Leave it to me.</b></font>

596
00:39:49,004 --> 00:39:51,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll buy our furniture from
the second-hand store online.</b></font>

597
00:39:51,444 --> 00:39:52,804
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's economical and practical.</b></font>

598
00:39:53,164 --> 00:39:56,444
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The most important thing is that
we're closer to Shancai's school.</b></font>

599
00:39:56,844 --> 00:39:59,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She can sleep half an hour more now.</b></font>

600
00:39:59,204 --> 00:40:00,164
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Am I right?</b></font>

601
00:40:00,244 --> 00:40:01,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Yes.
