602
00:40:02,444 --> 00:40:03,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You always think about our family.</b></font>

603
00:40:04,684 --> 00:40:05,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Marrying you</b></font>

604
00:40:05,604 --> 00:40:07,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>was the biggest blessing in my life.</b></font>

605
00:40:08,004 --> 00:40:09,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll do anything to make our family happy.</b></font>

606
00:40:10,444 --> 00:40:12,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Dear, I'll also work hard</b></font>

607
00:40:12,604 --> 00:40:14,724
<font color="#ffff00"><b>for you and our beloved daughter.</b></font>

608
00:40:15,164 --> 00:40:16,284
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I believe in you.</b></font>

609
00:40:16,884 --> 00:40:19,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-I'll also work hard.
