612
00:40:23,764 --> 00:40:24,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Yes?
-You can do it.</b></font>

613
00:40:24,684 --> 00:40:26,004
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-You can do it.
-I can do it.</b></font>

614
00:40:32,164 --> 00:40:34,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mom, I've already connected the water</b></font>

615
00:40:34,284 --> 00:40:35,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-and electricity--
