616
00:40:35,404 --> 00:40:36,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Check them--</b></font>

617
00:40:39,324 --> 00:40:40,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why didn't you say something?</b></font>

618
00:40:40,564 --> 00:40:42,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I called out to you.
