619
00:40:43,684 --> 00:40:44,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Nothing.</b></font>

620
00:40:45,884 --> 00:40:47,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You left these books at my house.</b></font>

621
00:40:48,524 --> 00:40:49,764
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I completely forgot about them.</b></font>

622
00:40:50,444 --> 00:40:52,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Bring your brain with you, will you?</b></font>

623
00:40:52,164 --> 00:40:53,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're always so absent-minded.</b></font>

624
00:40:55,324 --> 00:40:56,404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right.</b></font>

625
00:41:02,124 --> 00:41:03,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Did you forget something again?</b></font>

626
00:41:04,044 --> 00:41:05,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What?</b></font>

627
00:41:05,324 --> 00:41:07,884
<font color="#ffff00"><b>To say thank you.
