628
00:41:09,884 --> 00:41:10,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

629
00:41:16,884 --> 00:41:18,044
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>It's so strange.</i></b></font>

630
00:41:18,284 --> 00:41:20,644
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Why is he suddenly acting so normal again?</i></b></font>

631
00:41:21,204 --> 00:41:23,444
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Shouldn't he be ignoring me?</i></b></font>

632
00:41:33,644 --> 00:41:36,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Frankie Restaurant is looking
for a kitchen assistant.</b></font>

633
00:41:36,644 --> 00:41:37,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The hours...</b></font>

634
00:41:37,684 --> 00:41:39,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Six to ten at night.</b></font>

635
00:41:41,164 --> 00:41:42,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where is it?</b></font>

636
00:41:42,204 --> 00:41:43,444
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's near our school.</b></font>

637
00:41:44,404 --> 00:41:45,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's great.</b></font>

638
00:42:10,124 --> 00:42:11,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hi.</b></font>

639
00:42:11,364 --> 00:42:13,404
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm here to apply for the kitchen
assistant position.</b></font>

640
00:42:14,204 --> 00:42:15,524
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The kitchen is that way.</b></font>

641
00:42:16,004 --> 00:42:17,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

642
00:42:35,404 --> 00:42:36,444
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Who are you?</b></font>

643
00:42:37,084 --> 00:42:39,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well, I'm here to apply
