649
00:43:22,764 --> 00:43:24,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You got over Shancai in just a few days.</b></font>

650
00:43:25,084 --> 00:43:26,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Of course.</b></font>

651
00:43:26,284 --> 00:43:27,364
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What was I thinking?</b></font>

652
00:43:28,444 --> 00:43:30,044
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm completely over it now.</b></font>

653
00:43:30,244 --> 00:43:32,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Who wants such a cheap girl?</b></font>

654
00:43:32,164 --> 00:43:35,764
