655
00:43:40,484 --> 00:43:42,284
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Speak of the devil.</b></font>

656
00:43:43,124 --> 00:43:44,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Who told him to come here?</b></font>

657
00:43:52,684 --> 00:43:54,244
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you suddenly shooting pool?</b></font>

658
00:43:54,324 --> 00:43:55,164
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's been a while.</b></font>

659
00:43:56,964 --> 00:43:58,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's all because of Si.</b></font>

660
00:43:58,924 --> 00:44:01,164
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not sure what he's thinking.
