00:44:16,004 --> 00:44:17,924
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't mind him. He's always been that way.</b></font>

667
00:44:18,004 --> 00:44:19,484
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lei, how did it go last night?</b></font>

668
00:44:20,204 --> 00:44:21,084
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you mean?</b></font>

669
00:44:21,644 --> 00:44:23,204
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't play dumb. You and Shancai.</b></font>

