<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey, why aren't you answering?</b></font>

674
00:44:38,164 --> 00:44:39,324
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There's nothing to hide.</b></font>

675
00:44:41,404 --> 00:44:42,844
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai is a nice girl.</b></font>

676
00:44:44,004 --> 00:44:46,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I admit. I almost fell for her.</b></font>

677
00:44:48,164 --> 00:44:50,124
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But how do I say this?</b></font>

678
00:44:51,484 --> 00:44:52,964
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I won't do anything to her.</b></font>

679
00:44:55,364 --> 00:44:56,284
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why?</b></font>

680
00:44:56,884 --> 00:44:59,284
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because I won't betray Si.</b></font>

681
00:45:00,044 --> 00:45:01,604
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He's a good friend that we grew up with.</b></font>

682
00:45:02,724 --> 00:45:03,564
